32/*
33 * ex_version -- :version
34 * Display the program version.
35 *
36 * PUBLIC: int ex_version __P((SCR *, EXCMD *));
37 */
38int
39ex_version(SCR *sp, EXCMD *cmdp)
40{
41 msgq(sp, M_INFO, "Version "VI_VERSION
42 " The CSRG, University of California, Berkeley.");
43 return (0);
44}
